    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128010/extras/81b7d475dc2501822b3b56af0edef469.poster.avif?t=1730219571\" width=464 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128010/extras/81b7d475dc2501822b3b56af0edef469.webm?t=1730219571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128010/extras/81b7d475dc2501822b3b56af0edef469.mp4?t=1730219571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a world overrun by the undead in this gripping turn-based tactical roguelike. As a survivor, you'll fight off groups of zombies using different weapons in strategically intense, fast-paced battles. Every victory brings the chance to choose reward that will enhance your character's abilities. Each level becomes progressively harder, pushing your tactical skills to the limit. Can you outsmart the undead and emerge victorious in this thrilling fight for survival? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Levels</strong>: Experience a different challenge every time you play with procedurally generated levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tactical Turn-Based Combat</strong>: Plan your moves carefully and outmaneuver the zombies in tactical turn-based battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-Paced Gameplay</strong>: Engage in quick, intense skirmishes that keep you on the edge of your seat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character Progression</strong>: Pick one the random rewards after each battle to strengthen your character's abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Increasing Difficulty</strong>: Face tougher and more challenging enemies as you advance through the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128010/extras/751a91c016d578699895897dd0f0605b.poster.avif?t=1730219571\" width=458 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128010/extras/751a91c016d578699895897dd0f0605b.webm?t=1730219571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128010/extras/751a91c016d578699895897dd0f0605b.mp4?t=1730219571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
